    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Used by theater troupes in combination with a fake blood pack, this bit of minor magic can simulate a dramatic and sudden wound. A *blood pack squib* is a small unassuming stone that is keyed to a single fake blood pack in a process that takes 1 minute.",
